  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Clari is a charming Alpine hotel well-situated in a quiet area of town, yet only a short walk from the lifts and resort amenities - at the entrance to the village, approx 7 minutes’ walk (550m) to the lifts. The hotel also operates a free shuttle to and from the centre and lifts (9-10.30am &amp; 4-6pm). A welcome addition to our programme, this cosy and relaxed hotel excels in great hospitality alongside a good selection of facilities. These include wellness centre with sauna, steam room and whirlpool. </p>]]></description>
